Package: ramcacher
Title: In-Memory Caching for Functions and Expressions
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "De Meyer", , "sam.demeyer93@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Cache the results of functions and expressions in RAM for faster
    subsequent retrieval. Automatically detects when code or arguments change
    to invalidate stale cache entries. Provides utilities to manage cache
    entries including listing, getting, setting, and clearing cached values.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Imports: 
    digest,
    glue,
    rlang,
    stringr
